pharmacy:
    play sound click
    choice:
        "Your hormones await you at the chemist, supposedly."
        "[Visit the chemist] <span class='prompt'>[[-1 ACTION]]</span>" if (>= $stats.actions.value 1):
            play sound spendAction
            set data.game_map.inMap false
            add_stat actions -1
            set_button button_pharmacy false
            run transition_black pharmacy
            clear_dialog
        "<span class='prompt'>[[BACK]]</span>":
            jump game_map

    play sound bell
    if $data.global.hormonesLate:
        jump pharmacy_return
    else:
        "The chemist consists of a counter, and behind it a treasure trove."
        clear_dialog
    talk nasty talk "Prescription drugs awooooooo. Let's steal some adderall and go wild."
    clear_dialog
    "There she is, The Keeper of the Gate of Venus. In her little hands she clutches a copy of 'Hetero Weekly', Anglia's number one journal for heterosexual romance stories with happy endings. She occasionally titters or squeaks to herself as she reads it."
    if (roll pharmacy_magazine_orb orb 60):
        talk orb talk "<span class='writtenText'>'He held her breast in his strong, big hand. He was six foot seven, big and jacked. His girthy, big meat strained in his loins, desperate to splatter its seed betwixt her smooth, big, supple orbs.</span>"
    else:
        wait 1000
    clear_dialog
    "The Keeper of the Gate seems to sense your approach, and it annoys her. She closes the magazine, but keeps hold of it."
    if (roll pharmacy_magazine_lovely lovely 40):
        talk lovely talk "She's hoping you'll go away fast enough that she need not put it down."
    else:
        wait 1000
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk gatekeeper talkalt "Hello sir, how can I help you today?"
        "\\"It's Mam actually.\\"":
            choice:
                talk gatekeeper talkalt "Oops! Sorry sir! I'll keep that in mind."
                "\\"No see look, you just did it again!\\"":
                    choice:
                        talk gatekeeper talkalt "Did what?"
                        "\\"Called me sir! It's mam!\\"":
                            talk gatekeeper talkalt "Oh! I'm sorry, silly me! I can be ever such a ditz sometimes!"
                            clear_dialog
                            "She titters cheerily."
                "\\"Never mind.\\"":
                    "The Keeper of the Gate nods."
            if (roll pharmacy_sir_lovely lovely 40):
                talk lovely talk "She's not doing it on purpose. She's just dense."
            else:
                wait 1000
        "\\"Don't I know you?\\"":
            talk gatekeeper talkalt "No? I don't believe so?"
            clear_dialog
            talk orb talk "She *does* seem familiar..."
    clear_dialog
    talk gatekeeper talkalt "Anyway, how can I help you today, sir?"
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        "The keeper of the gate peers into your eyes. Her judgement nestles itself in the folds of your iris like cum in a twinks cum gutter."
        "\\"I'm here to pick up a prescription.\\" [Do a gay little nod]":
            "She sighs, and puts down her magazine."
        "\\"I think the *real* question is what can you do for *me*.\\"":
            choice:
                talk gatekeeper talkalt "That's essentially what I asked, yes. Do you need to pick up a prescription?"
                "[Stare forlornly at your feet, defeated] \\"Yes mam.\\"":
                    "She sighs and puts down her magazine."
                "[Stare forlornly at your feet, defeated] \\"Yes mam. I'm not into feet, by the way, I'm only looking at them because I feel silly. Normally I'd not make a big deal of it, it's just there's been a lot of disinformation flying around about me as of late...\\"":
                    set data.ghost.footGirl true
                    talk gatekeeper talkalt "Right. Okay sir."
                    clear_dialog
                    "She puts down her magazine."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk gatekeeper talkalt "May I ask what you need the prescription for?"
        "\\"I'm a type VI Transexual babey!!!\\"":
            jump pharmacy_warning
        "\\"Um. You may not?\\"":
            play sound knife
            run transition_pain
            "Her glare teleports behind you and bisects your soul."
            if (roll pharmacy_job_orb orb 20):
                talk orb talk "She doesn't have any recourse for this. She was vouching on you assuming she had the right to know, which she doesn't."
            else:
                wait 1000
            clear_dialog
            talk gatekeeper talkalt "I was only trying to make conversation. No need to get snappy, sir."
            jump pharmacy_prescription
        "\\"Why?\\"":
            talk gatekeeper talkalt "Because it's my job."
            if (roll pharmacy_job_orb orb 20):
                talk orb talk "It isn't."
            else:
                wait 1000
            clear_dialog
            choice:
                "The Keeper of the Gate does not break eye contact. She wants to know what your prescription is for more than she wants anything else in the world."
                "\\"I'm a type VI Transexual babey!!!\\"":
                    jump pharmacy_warning
                "\\"Can I please just have my prescription please?\\"":
                    play sound knife
                    run transition_pain
                    "Her glare teleports behind you and bisects your soul."
                    clear_dialog
                    talk gatekeeper talkalt "One of those, types, hmm? Fine."
                    jump pharmacy_prescription
    
pharmacy_warning:
    set data.pharmacy_warned true
    talk gatekeeper talkalt "Ohhhh you're one of *those*! Well, if that's the case..."
    clear_dialog
    "She breathes in deeply, edging you."
    clear_dialog
    talk gatekeeper talkalt "I need to walk you through the side effects of this stuff! It can be pretty dangerous, you know?"
    if (roll pharmacy_warning_danger_orb orb 1):
        talk orb talk "It really isn't."
    else:
        wait 1000
    if (roll pharmacy_warning_danger_nightmare nightmare 20):
        talk nightmare talk "<span class='nightmare'>it really is.</span>"
    else:
        wait 1000
    clear_dialog
    play sound static
    "She opens her mouth, and a sound like radio static fills the air. Minutes pass."
    clear_dialog
    "When she finally closes her mouth, the sound ceases."
    "She leans in close, and as a thin trickle of murky brown liquid trickles from the corner of her mouth she whispers."
    clear_dialog
    talk gatekeeper talkalt "And oh..."
    clear_dialog
    "She peers at you over her glasses. Her hollow stare hits you like a pair of anti-tank shells colliding directly with your eye sockets. This is the big one."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk gatekeeper talkalt "One of the many, *many* negative side effects, is that you *will* experience permanent breast growth."
        "[Nod] \\"Noted.\\"":
            run skip
        "\\"I know. I already know this. I've used this before. I literally have tits from using this before.\\"":
            talk gatekeeper talkalt "Well I'm just looking out for your health."
            clear_dialog
            "Her voice snaps like a ruler against your cheek."
            if (roll pharmacy_warning_mad_lovely lovely 20):
                talk lovely talk "She's genuinely mad at you for saying that. She was trying to help you."
            else:
                wait 1000
        "\\"Damn that would really suck if that wasn't literally the reason I need this, thanks for the warning.\\"":
            talk gatekeeper talkalt "It really would!"
            clear_dialog
            talk lovely talk "She didn't catch onto your sarcasm, because she's really quite stupid."
        "\\"Awooga! Hubba hubba! That bops.\\"":
            "She ignores you."
    jump pharmacy_prescription

pharmacy_prescription:
    clear_dialog
    if $data.pharmacy_warned:
        choice:
            talk gatekeeper talkalt "Anyway, I'll go get your prescription, but may my warning stay with you, and forget not my words."
            "\\"I'll do my best but I can't promise anything given that my memory isn't the bes- well, it isn't, right now.\\"":
                "She nods, and heads to the storage area behind the counter."
            "\\"I won't.\\"":
                "She nods, and heads to the storage area behind the counter."
            "\\"Sorry, could you repeat that, I forgot what you said.\\"":
                "The gate keeper huffs huffily."
                clear_dialog
                talk gatekeeper talkalt "I said <span class='writtenText'>'Anyway, I'll go get your prescription. But let my warning stay with you, and forget not my words.'</span>"
                clear_dialog
                "She heads to the storage area behind the counter."
    else:
        talk gatekeeper talkalt "Anyway, I'll go get your prescription."
        clear_dialog
        "She heads to the storage area behind the counter."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk gatekeeper talkalt "What's your name, sir?"
        "\\"It's Ghost.\\"" if (!= $data.ghost.nameGhosty true):
            talk gatekeeper talkalt "Ghost... Okay Mister Ghost, I'll be right back."
        "\\"It's Ghost Ghosty.\\"" if $data.ghost.nameGhosty:
            talk gatekeeper talkalt "Ghost Ghosty... Okay Mister Ghosty, I'll be right back."
    clear_dialog
    if $data.nkvd.gatekeeperWaited:
        jump pharmacy_recieve
    else:
        "She looks around in the way someone might look around if they heard a faint, distant sound, but not care enough to actually find its source. A big exclamation mark appears above her head and she starts doing an idle 'searching' animation that loops slightly too quickly to look natural and appears to be missing the last few frames that complete the loop anyway. A few seconds later she snaps back to normal."
        clear_dialog
        talk gatekeeper talkalt "I'm not seeing any prescriptions back here for a mister <span class='writtenText'>'Ghost'</span>."
        clear_dialog
        choice:
            "She starts eating one of her fingers and squeaking."
            "\\"Can you see any for a *Ms* Ghost?\\"":
                "The Keeper of the Gate scans around again, her eyes squinting so hard they look fit to burst."
                clear_dialog
                talk gatekeeper talkalt "No, I don't see any for your sister either."
            "\\"Damn that sucks. Guess I'll die.\\"":
                "The Keeper of the Gate either ignores your melodrama, or does not hear it."
                if (roll pharmacy_prescription_ignored_lovely lovely 20):
                    talk lovely talk "She isn't paying attention to you."
                else:
                    wait 1000
        clear_dialog
        talk gatekeeper talkalt "I'd recommend talking to your healthcare practise, perhaps they simply forgot to send the prescription through?"
        if $data.nkvd.one_gatekeeper_wait:
            talk orb talk "Gods dammit, I told you Ghost."
        clear_dialog
        choice:
            talk orb talk "I suppose we should head back to the *other* Keeper of the Gate of Venus. How annoying. That place closes pretty early, hopefully not already..."
            "\\"I'll go talk to the other one of you. Thank you. Thankssss.\\"":
                talk gatekeeper talkalt "Mhm."
            "\\"Finally. A quest worthy of me.\\" [Raise one of your hands aloft as though holding a mighty sword] \\"I will journey to the gate of Venus and slay the other Keeper of the Gate, who so cruelly betrayed me.\\" [Leave]":
                talk lovely talk "Wheeee! How dashing you are, Ghost!"
                clear_dialog
                talk gatekeeper talkalt "Okay sir."
        clear_dialog
        choice:
            "The Keeper of the Gate is ignoring you in favour of her magazine, again."
            "[Leave the chemist] <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>]":
                play sound spendAction
                play sound bell
                if (== $stats.day.value 2):
                    set data.global.hrt_nextStageDay 3
                if (== $stats.day.value 3):
                    set data.global.hrt_nextStageDay 4
                if (== $stats.day.value 4):
                    set data.global.hrt_nextStageDay 5
                complete_objective hrt pharmacy
                start_objective hrt keeper
                "You step outside the chemist with a big healthcare system shaped hole in your heart."
                if (roll pharmacy_prescription_circle_orb orb 20):
                    talk orb talk "It's a circle, actually. I am a sphere."
                else:
                    wait 1000
                jump goToGameMap

pharmacy_return:
    "Entering the chemist you can see that The Keeper of the Gate of Venus has resumed her post. She is still reading the same issue of Hetero Monthly."
    if (roll pharmacy_return_magazine_orb orb 20):
        talk orb talk "She's on her fifth reread."
        if (roll pharmacy_return_magazine_nasty nasty 20):
            talk nasty talk "She really likes the story about the heteros banging in a barn."
            if (roll pharmacy_return_barn_orb orb 60):
                talk orb talk "Nasty Girl's right. She loves it. She loves barn sex."
                clear_dialog
                talk nasty talk "Looks like she has *some* amount of good taste, ey ladies?"
                talk lovely talk "Ghastly. I think I'd rather die than have intercourse in a 'barn'."
                talk nasty talk "Yeah? How about a... I don't know... stable?"
                talk lovely talk "Gasp!"
            else:
                wait 1000
        else:
            wait 1000
    else:
        wait 1000
    clear_dialog
    "The Keeper of the Gate looks up from her magazine. She heard you enter, and she's *very* annoyed at you for doing so."
    clear_dialog
    talk gatekeeper talkalt "Oh, it's you, mister... um... Ghost, yes?"
    if (roll pharmacy_return_pride_lovely lovely 20):
        talk lovely talk "She's genuinely proud of herself for remembering your name."
    else:
        wait 1000
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk gatekeeper talkalt "How can I help you?"
        "\\"Hello again. Can I have my prescription now? Assuming the other Gatekeeper actually sent you the request I mean.\\"":
            choice:
                talk gatekeeper talkalt "Of course sir. May I ask your name?"
                "\\"Didn't you literally just call me by my name a few moments ago?\\"":
                    choice:
                        talk gatekeeper talkalt "I don't think so sir, name?"
                        "\\"It's Ghost.\\"" if (!= $data.ghost.nameGhosty true):
                            talk gatekeeper talkalt "Mhm. Let me take a look."
                        "\\"It's Ghost. Same as yesterday.\\"" if (!= $data.ghost.nameGhosty true):
                            talk gatekeeper talkalt "Mhm. Let me take a look."
                        "\\"It's Ghost Ghosty.\\"" if $data.ghost.nameGhosty:
                            talk gatekeeper talkalt "Mhm. Let me take a look."
                        "\\"It's Ghost Ghosty. Same as yesterday.\\"" if $data.ghost.nameGhosty:
                            talk gatekeeper talkalt "Mhm. Let me take a look."
    jump pharmacy_recieve

pharmacy_recieve:
    clear_dialog
    "The Keeper of the Gate of Venus begins to fumble about behind the counter."
    "She's playing a xylophone and making her mouth go pop pop pop. She starts practising a new whisker bopping dance. She writes a seven-hundred-page novel. She reads The Daily Moon, headline today: <span class='writtenText'>'Win for Bluehills! New trainline would cut costs, lower journey time and reduce local automobile dependency. This project we can confirm has been cancelled after the valiant efforts of the Bluehills Homeowner Group'</span>. She runs in circles going 'wheeee!'. She picks up a big piece of glass and smashes her head through it, as a bit."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        "Eventually, she picks up the paper bag containing you prescription, and walks back over to you."
        "\\"Thanks.\\"":
            "The Keeper of the Gate sneezes on you."
        "\\"Thanks?\\"":
            "The Keeper of the Gate sneezes on you."
        "\\"Did that have to take so long?\\"":
            talk gatekeeper talkalt "Hmm? Yes."
            clear_dialog
            "She sneezes on you."
    clear_dialog
    talk gatekeeper talkalt "Achoo! Bless me."
    clear_dialog
    "She titters to herself."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk gatekeeper talkalt "That'll be twenty pounds please."
        "\\"I thought Anglian healthcare was free?\\"":
            choice:
                talk gatekeeper talkalt "It is free, yes, you just have to pay for it."
                "\\"I'm not sure you understand what free means.\\"":
                    talk gatekeeper talkalt "The healthcare costs nothing but the medication costs twenty pounds."
        "\\"There's a pride parade this week. Does that mean I can have them for free, on account of me being a bit fruity?\\"":
            choice:
                talk gatekeeper talkalt "No."
                "[Shake your head] \\"And on pride week too...\\"":
                    run skip
    clear_dialog
    "The Keeper of the Gate wiggles the fingers of her little outstretched hand."
    jump pharmacy_pay

pharmacy_pay:
    if (>= $stats.money.value 20):
        choice:
            "You rummage through your bag and fish out twenty Anglian pounds. The face of Saint Dawnsight looks up at you. 'I am a coin' her eyes seem to say. You nod. She is."
            "\\"Here's twenty pounds.\\" [Hand over twenty pounds]":
                add_stat money -20
                play sound coins
                jump pharmacy_conclusion
            "\\"Actually, I think I'll keep hold of this. I'm thinking of investing in daffodil bulbs, in case they go jump in value again.\\"" if $data.global.daffodilFact:
                "The Keeper of the Gate frowns."
            "\\"Actually, I think I'll keep hold of this. I might need it for... spending...\\"":
                "The Keeper of the Gate frowns."
            roll pharmacy_prescription_steal_nasty nasty 40 "[Literally just grab the little paper bag of hormones and run]":
                success "":
                    play sound footstepsinside
                    "You grab the bag and leg it, deftly jumping over a spilt container of lube that you would have fallen over had you failed the skill check."
                    "You scamper out of the door and into the wide wild world."
                    jump pharmacy_stealSuccess
                failure "":
                    play sound punch
                    run transition_pain
                    "You slip on a split container of lube, and faceplant directly into the floor. You drop the hormones and see three little birdies and a feathery biplane start tweeting and fluttering around your head as your eyes spin."
                    if (roll pharmacy_stealFail_birds_orb orb 20):
                        talk orb talk "Those birds aren't real. You're hallucinating."
                    else:
                        wait 1000
                    jump pharmacy_stealFailure
            roll pharmacy_prescription_steal_nasty nasty 60 "[Literally just grab the little paper bag of hormones and run but then stop at the door to flip The Keeper of the Gate off before leaving]":
                success "":
                    play sound footstepsinside
                    "The door shuts just in time for you to see the bemused look on the Gatekeepers face. She is livid."
                    jump pharmacy_stealSuccess
                failure "":
                    play sound punch
                    run transition_pain
                    "Unfortunately, the door closes on you outstretched wrist, and you scream, letting the bag of hormones drop to the floor. The door didn't hit you hard, you're just very pathetic."
                    jump pharmacy_stealFailure
        talk gatekeeper talkalt "Did you just come here to waste my time?"
        clear_dialog
        choice:
            talk orb talk "Did you just come here to waste *our* time, Ghost? Buy the fucking hormones you stupid bitch."
            "An eloquently stated argument, Orb. [Hand over twenty pounds]":
                add_stat money -20
                play sound coins
                jump pharmacy_conclusion
            "I want to keep hold of my money, what are you, the taxman here to steal my precious emeralds? I'm going to horde it in an offshore bank account and swim around in it when the interest grows this humble handful of coins into a veritable lake of wealth, and *you* are not invited!":
                talk orb talk "Ghost what the fuck are you on about? Has Lovely Lady been talking to you about tax evasion behind my back?"
                talk lovely talk "Just as rules were made to be broken taxes were made to be evaded. How else would Papis emerald mine have made us so thoroughly comfortable?"
                clear_dialog
                choice:
                    talk gatekeeper talkalt "Sir, do you want the prescription or not?"
                    "\\"Yes please.\\" [Hand over twenty pounds]":
                        talk gatekeeper talkalt "Right. I'm glad we've clarified that."
                        add_stat money -20
                        play sound coins
                        jump pharmacy_conclusion
                    "[Storm out of the chemist ranting about how the healthcare industry will never get its claws on your precious emeralds]":
                        choice:
                            talk orb talk "Sigh. What a mess you've made, Ghost."
                            "Now how can I get hold or hormones? Without handing over my emeralds, I mean.":
                                jump keeper_alternatives
    else:
        choice:
            "You rummage through your bag and find you do not have enough pennies to pay for your medication. The Keeper of the Gate of Venus eyes you suspiciously."
            "\\"Could I have it for free please?\\"":
                talk gatekeeper talkalt "You may not."
                jump pharmacy_pay
            roll pharmacy_prescription_steal_nasty nasty 40 "[Literally just grab the little paper bag of hormones and run]":
                success "":
                    play sound footstepsinside
                    "You grab the bag and leg it, deftly jumping over a spilt container of lube that you would have fallen over had you failed the previous skill check."
                    clear_dialog
                    talk gatekeeper talkalt "H- hey!"
                    clear_dialog
                    jump pharmacy_stealSuccess
                failure "":
                    play sound punch
                    run transition_pain
                    "You slip on a split container of lube, and faceplant directly into the floor. You drop the hormones and see three little birdies start tweeting and fluttering around your head as your eyes spin."
                    if (roll pharmacy_stealFail_birds_orb orb 20):
                        talk orb talk "Those birds aren't real. You're hallucinating."
                    else:
                        wait 1000
                    jump pharmacy_stealFailure
            roll pharmacy_prescription_steal_nasty nasty 60 "[Literally just grab the little paper bag of hormones and run but then stop at the door to flip The Keeper of the Gate off before leaving]":
                success "":
                    play sound footstepsinside
                    "You grab the bag and leg it, making sure to stop so you can sling a final insult at the Keeper of the Gate."
                    clear_dialog
                    talk gatekeeper talkalt "H- hey!"
                    clear_dialog
                    jump pharmacy_stealSuccess
                failure "":
                    play sound punch
                    run transition_pain
                    "Unfortunately, the door closes on you outstretched wrist, and you scream, letting the bag of hormones drop to the floor. The door didn't hit you hard, you're just very pathetic."
                    jump pharmacy_stealFailure
            "\\"I guess I'll come back later.\\" [Sigh] \\"What is a little lady to do in this economy?\\"":
                choice:
                    talk gatekeeper talkalt "He is to bring money with her when she comes to the chemist. Bye now."
                    "\\"Bye, I guess...\\" [Leave the chemist] <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
                        play sound spendAction
                        play sound bell
                        jump goToGameMap

pharmacy_conclusion:     
    clear_dialog
    add_item hrt 1 
    if (!= (objective_completed? hrt pharmacy) true):
        complete_objective hrt pharmacy
    if (objective_started? hrt pharmacyReturn):
        complete_objective hrt pharmacyReturn
    complete_objective hrt hrt
    "The Keeper of the Gate spends about five minutes counting the twenty coins you hand her. She keeps dropping the pennies / accidentality swallowing them and needing you to perform the heimlich manoeuvrer on her etc."
    "When she is eventually satisfied you haven't tried to short-change her or otherwise fool her with chocolate coins (she checks via nibble), The Keeper of the Gate of Venus hands you the paper bag."
    clear_dialog
    if $data.pharmacy_warning:
        talk gatekeeper talkalt "Have a nice day, sir. Enjoy your feminising hormones."
    else:
        talk gatekeeper talkalt "Have a nice day now, sir."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        "She picks up her magazine and returns to her tales of softcore, chaste, heterosexual fucking."
        "\\"Thank you. Bye.\\" [Do a gay little curtsey] <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
            play sound spendAction
            play sound bell
            start_objective hrt usehrt
            "You step outside the chemist with a big healthcare system shaped plaster taped over your heart."
            jump goToGameMap

pharmacy_stealSuccess:
    play sound bell
    clear_dialog
    add_item hrt 1 
    if (!= (objective_completed? hrt pharmacy) true):
        complete_objective hrt pharmacy
    if (objective_started? hrt pharmacyReturn):
        complete_objective hrt pharmacyReturn
    complete_objective hrt hrt
    run transition generic_street
    choice:
        "You run randomly through the streets, until you're pretty content that the rozzers aren't on your tail."
        "Awoooo! We did it! I'm so cool! I love crime now! Awoooo!":
            unlock_achievement thief
            talk nasty talk "Awooooo!"
    clear_dialog
    talk lovely talk "I take absolutely no ownership over this nonsense."
    talk orb talk "This isn't exactly a long-term solution to this problem, but I suppose the fact you gave them the name <span class='writtenText'>'Ghost'</span> means the repercussions of this will never catch up to you, so there's that."
    talk nasty talk "Unless Ghost is her real name..."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk orb talk "Ghost, you realise you can *never* come back here, don't you?"
        "Worth it. That was the perfect crime. <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
            play sound spendAction
            start_objective hrt usehrt
            talk nasty talk "Let's head home and try this bad boy out."
            jump goToGameMap

pharmacy_stealFailure:
    set data.nkvd.stealFail true
    clear_dialog
    talk gatekeeper talkalt "Sir! I *will* call for the police!"
    clear_dialog
    "She picks up her telephone, realises it isn't plugged in, and then just shouts really loudly."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk gatekeeper talkalt "POLICE! WE HAVE A CRIMINAL HERE!"
        "[Almost have a panic attack, despite the lack of actual danger and scamper away from the chemist, forgetting to pick up your hormones]":
            play sound bell
            clear_dialog
            run transition generic_street
            "You eventually find yourself narrowly avoiding an asthma attack some distance away from the chemist."
            "There aren't any rozzers following you, so you're probably safe."
    clear_dialog
    talk nasty talk "Wow. That fucking sucked. We're so bad at crime."
    talk lovely talk "I take absolutely no ownership over this nonsense."
    clear_dialog
    talk orb talk "I suppose the fact you gave them the name <span class='writtenText'>'Ghost'</span> means the repercussions of this will never catch up to you, so there's that."
    talk nasty talk "Unless Ghost is her real name."
    choice:
        talk orb talk "Unless Ghost is her real name, yes."
        "This does *not* bop! Now how do I get hormones?":
            if (!= (objective_completed? hrt pharmacy) true):
                complete_objective hrt pharmacy
            if (objective_started? hrt pharmacyReturn):
                complete_objective hrt pharmacyReturn
            jump keeper_alternatives